data.description: Welcome home to this adorable 2 bed, 1 bath ranch in sought after Leominster! Enter into the sun filled living room, where the gas fireplace sets the tone for a comfrotable and inviting space. The dine-in kitchen, seamlessly connected to the laundry/utility area also leads to a screened-in porch – an ideal sunny haven for enjoying a warm beverage and captivating read.The two bedrooms are complete with ample closets and cozy wall-to-wall carpeting.  Outside you will discover a wooden deck, perfect for al fresco dining and entertaining. The above-ground pool provides a refreshing escape during the warmer months, creating a private oasis for relaxation. Additional perks include a convenient storage shed, a firepit, and a fenced yard. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own – schedule a showing today!
